    • checkForErrorInInput2

      private boolean checkForErrorInInput2(LocalDate selectedDate, javafx.scene.control.TextField firstName, javafx.scene.control.TextField lastName, javafx.scene.control.TextField locations, javafx.scene.control.TextField instructorName, javafx.scene.control.TextField className, javafx.scene.control.RadioButton memberCheck, javafx.scene.control.RadioButton guestCheck, Member member, FitnessClass fitnessClassWNoTime)
      Checks if when a user adds a checks in or checks out a member/guest, if the inputted information for a member is valid (helper method for checkInToFitnessClass() checkOutOfFitnessClass()).
      Parameters:
      selectedDate - the selected date from the DatePicker.
      firstName - the inputted first name in the text field.
      lastName - the inputted last name in the text field.
      locations - the inputted location name in the text field.
      instructorName - the inputted instructor name in the text field.
      className - the inputted class name in the text field.
      memberCheck - the radio button for if checking in/out a member is selected.
      guestCheck - the radio button for if checking in/out a guest is selected.
      member - the created member based on what the user entered.
      fitnessClassWNoTime - the created fitness class based on what the user entered.
      Returns:
      true if there was an error, false otherwise.
